  <name>Composer</name>
  <summary>Download lyrics files for your music collection</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Composer is a modern GNOME/Adwaita application designed to help music enthusiasts manage lyrics for their music library. It provides an intuitive interface for scanning music directories, extracting metadata from audio files, and managing lyrics files. Currently it features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Search and download lyrics for your music files</li>
      <li>Romanization support for non-Latin script lyrics</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

